{"tid":2048104,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"維吉尼亞州列治文警察局長：左派暴徒縱火焚燒裡面有兒童的房子，然後封鎖消防局","createTime":"2020-06-02T14:33:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-02T14:33:35.000Z","uid":233530,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"dc3999330566737a4df020e5166cb776f19fffc7","tid":2048104,"uid":233530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T14:33:35.000Z","msg":"2020-5-31 May 31, 2020 at 1:44 PM EDT - Updated May 31 at 4:01 PM<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nbc12.com/2020/05/31/its-unacceptable-richmond-police-chief-gets-emotional-while-talking-about-protests/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbc12.com%2F2020%2F05%2F31%2Fits-unacceptable-richmond-police-chief-gets-emotional-while-talking-about-protests%2F&d=9MYRmPDtC2YjWedq%2F%2FxxgfsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=3a639536\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nbc12.com/2020/05/31/its-unacceptable-richmond-police-chief-gets-emotional-while-talking-about-protests/</a><br />\n列治文市警察局局長威爾&middot;史密斯（Will Smith）在該市抗議活動的第二天晚上舉行的新聞發布會上激動不已。史密斯說，昨晚抗議者放火燒毀了幾座建築物，包括在西布羅德街區一個有孩子的多戶住宅。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.thegatewaypundit.com/wp-content/uploads/chief-william-smith-600x444.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thegatewaypundit.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fchief-william-smith-600x444.jpg&h=275f284d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n史密斯說，當消防人員趕到時，示威者阻止發動機到達火場。<br />\n&ldquo;當您提出合理的問題但出於未知原因劫持它時，這對我來說是不可接受的，對於列治文警察局來說是不可接受的，對於列治文市來說是不可接受的。&rdquo;<br />\n警察很幸運地進了住宅裡營救孩子和他們的家人。<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.co/jvzqcaRA3i\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FjvzqcaRA3i&d=9MYRmPDtC2YjWedq%2F%2FxxgfsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=639f13ca\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.co/jvzqcaRA3i</a>"}]}